content.div:
It has been three months since we announced the engagement of Jessica Biel and her on-off man of five years, Justin Timberlake -- and actress is now finally showing off her GIANT rock! Click here to see it.

Biel and Timberlake were spotted chowing down on sandwiches at L.A. hotspot Tavern on Thursday, when a lucky pap snapped a photo of the vintage-looking bauble.

According to People, the pair met up with another couple and their toddler and was all smiles during lunch. Biel and Timberlake were later spotted leaving the eatery, he in a checkered shirt paired with a paperboy cap, and she in a gorgeous aqua dress accessorized with her giant rock.

The rock is a knock-out. It’s rounded square diamond is surrounded with smaller stones. Sources inside the restaurant told People that the pair was very sweet to each other and their friends' tot. The source also added that Biel “could not have looked happier.”

This isn't the first time that Biel has showed off her new bauble. The actress was spotted in February at a Saturday Night Live after party in New York City, where she showed it off to Amy Poehler and Kristen Wiig -- but managed to keep it away from the lens of the paps.

Biel's New Year’s Eve and Valentine's Day director, Garry Marshall, recently told Us Weekly of the engagement, "We talk about it a lot. I hope it all works out -- they are terrific kids. I love them both. I'm happy for her."
